{
  "stem": "322.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was not on my mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just like my father said.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't think of your mother and your sisters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Survive.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I did what he wanted me to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you want to know the real truth?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I often wonder why it was necessary for me to have survived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when cruelty-- you speak of cruelty in that way, you-- sometimes you will even refer to, you know, to, to your Almighty, to God, and ask Him, why did He have to be so cruel and leave me here?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] That's the only thing that I cannot level with.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[CRYING] I cannot understand that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Why did it have to be me of all of the six?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this is-- to this day, I keep asking myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It's not a-- it's not something to be thankful about, although I can be told differently by others.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it's my conviction, when that happens to a family, it should happen to all if it needs to be happening.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I could never live that off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] it's not easy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "50 years-- I've lived 50 years after that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Can you-- anybody even believe that it would be possible to live 50 more years with such awesomeness, with that knowledge [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that He took them, but He wouldn't take me?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you offered me another 50 years, no, thanks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It's not, not an easy thing to deal with.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when they're asking us to tell those who would like to know what this barbaric event was all about, we can tell, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] but there is no way they'll ever understand it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's useless.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
